Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.11,0:00:19.44,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.81,0:00:25.26,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.54,0:00:31.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:37.21,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.53,0:00:43.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.55,0:00:49.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:53.13,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:58.23,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.50,0:01:01.49,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.73,0:01:06.86,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.18,0:01:12.88,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,that blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:18.37,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:24.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:38.93,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(76,130)}PINEAPPLE SALAD
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:01:59.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about pathetic.\NJeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.17,0:02:01.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:02.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.73,0:02:07.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor said your wounds aren't serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.38,0:02:09.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But given their location,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:13.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,he wants to keep you in the hospital until\Nwe get more detailed results back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.67,0:02:14.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.07,0:02:16.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,With head wounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,it's not uncommon for people to feel fine\Nat first but suddenly drop dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:20.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop trying to scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.11,0:02:23.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just for four or five days.\NWell, I'll see you in four hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.43,0:02:43.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:44.90,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.00,0:02:49.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault that you were hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:57.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.45,0:03:03.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... You've never said,\N"I'm sorry" to me before, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:11.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's clear that my orders are\Nto blame for what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.35,0:03:14.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:20.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were a better pilot, then I wouldn't get\Nhurt no matter what orders you gave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:21.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've lost my confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:29.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NThis isn't like you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:39.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't leave the bridge unattended,\Nso I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:40.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get well soon, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:42.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:47.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So you do know the word "thanks."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop moping around.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:11.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy's injuries weren't serious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:16.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing happened to\Nme once, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:20.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The first time I met Focker, my heart\Nkind of went "twang..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even at work, my head was full of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And no matter what I did,\NI just couldn't focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I had it pretty bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:30.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make it sound like I'm\Na robot or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:34.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough about that.\NHow'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:38.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you tell the boy how you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:39.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:43.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry that he's younger than you.\NJust come out and say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:46.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It's not like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.59,0:04:50.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, whatever.\NJust stop moping, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:51.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:55.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,With as many people as we have on board,\Nsupplies can be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:58.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How long will we be staying here, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:01.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we've finished taking on supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:02.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and I gave Captain Hayase\Na stern lecture
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:09.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,about not letting her personal feelings\Ninterfere with her work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:14.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering what I saw when I came in,\Nit might have been a little too stern.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:19.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zero-g love, zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:23.04,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Zero-g love, zero-g love!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.11,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:29.20,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With him after school, on my way home
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:25.95,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a big star.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:28.08,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's getting farther and\Nfarther away...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:31.01,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,How depressing.\NNo matter what I try, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:35.91,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At the corner of that same old intersection
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:34.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hikaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:35.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:41.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He made sure no one else was around
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why so glum?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:40.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a get-well present.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:44.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice! You've even got Minmay\Nsinging to you in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.31,0:05:45.12,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then without warning, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.69,0:05:46.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:47.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to pay {\i1}me{\i0} a visit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:51.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but... C'mon, don't look at me\Nall scary like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:54.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad you weren't hurt too badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:56.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now take your mind off of things\Nand just get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:58.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the last thing I feel like doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.47,0:06:01.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotta get it together, Leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:03.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, getting hurt in an attack\Nlike that is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:05.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:10.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over for me when my\Nown men talk to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.15,0:06:11.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:14.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, we're gunnin' to \Nbecome leaders ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:17.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.57,0:06:20.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be in here forever if\Nthese two stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:22.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:25.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen you're alive, so I guess I can relax now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:28.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are some lovely flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:31.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Minmay must have been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.95,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like she'd ever show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.18,0:06:35.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a big star now.\NShe doesn't have the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:36.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you have a point!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.90,0:06:37.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.80,0:06:38.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:40.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they must be from Capt. Hayase, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:53.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He seemed worse off mentally than physically.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:07:00.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one specific medicine\Nthat'll cheer him up at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Specific medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:16.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is this business or pleasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I had to say, it's a bit of both.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:20.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.75,0:07:26.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I checked out Minmay's schedule, and today\Nshe's on the set filming her first movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.22,0:07:29.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The set, huh?\NOkay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.46,0:07:32.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to ask you to run errands\Nfor me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:34.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:36.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, can I tell you what\NI want in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:37.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:41.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just learned how to make\Na pineapple salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:43.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?\NWould you like to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:46.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.\NI'll drop by once I'm off duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.84,0:07:47.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.44,0:07:48.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.47,0:07:50.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm after a busy lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:53.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If she goes someplace else,\NI won't be able to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:54.31,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.01,0:08:07.19,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:12.55,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:10.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get your brand-new Minmay dolls right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Buy one now before they're sold out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.47,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shining, making a rapid descent
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.60,0:08:18.88,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then BOOM! he makes a sudden climb
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:25.10,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leaving a long trail of vapor
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What an amazing device!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:26.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow... I've got to have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:29.28,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He traces two big hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.32,0:08:29.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A Minmay doll... I want one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:32.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't push!\NDon't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:38.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!\NMy stock's all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:44.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That disco's nice, but it's always\Nthe same guys there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:45.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're all posers, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The guys there are all idiots.\NNo {\i1}way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:56.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We got away!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:58.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That worked great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:08:59.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man didn't even notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And now for the spoils of war!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:03.46,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoosh, whoosh! Whoosh, whoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:08.01,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My boyfriend is a pilot
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.79,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shining, making a rapid descent
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:15.37,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then BOOM! he makes a sudden climb
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a Minmay doll you're hiding, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:13.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:15.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!\NThey saw right through us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.94,0:09:19.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bad people! You took that\Nfrom some child, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all!\NThis is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:23.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!\NYou're into high school girls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:24.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,High school girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:27.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb!\NI'm gonna poke you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:33.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you guys around here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:36.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we've been around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.73,0:09:39.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We, uh, well, we work over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:44.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?\NAt the disco?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:47.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!\NThat's the disco we always go to!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:49.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's a "disco"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:54.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about convenient!\NLet's go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:57.33,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We were on our way there\Nourselves. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.85,0:09:59.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect, it's three on three.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:01.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, hurry!\NFever! Fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:02.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:07.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking to women without permission\Nis a court-martial offense!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:09.21,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for our mission.\NIt can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:09.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:25.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! What gives you the\Nright to lecture me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:29.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just saying you should feel\Nashamed to be a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:34.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get cocky! You came strolling up to the\Nfront line after we had already done all the work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.47,0:10:37.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten? The only reason\Nyou can mouth off now
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:40.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,is because we were there to\Nhaul you out of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:42.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:46.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to enjoy bragging about how\Nyou've never been defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:47.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but let me tell you something:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:51.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,the Macross has an ace pilot of its own!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.74,0:10:53.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,An ace pilot on the Macross?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.\NI'll take him on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:11.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Focker!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:21.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're making a kung fu movie!\NI'm the star!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:23.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You look so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.81,0:11:26.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to cheer me on, right?\NWhere's Hikaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:30.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I came here about Hikaru,\Nand to ask a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.40,0:11:31.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Hikaru all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:35.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He was injured in combat.\NHe's in the hospital right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:39.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you could\Nstop by and see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he badly hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:44.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not serious, but he's really\Ndown in the dumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:48.85,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured seeing your face\Nmight cheer him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:50.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:54.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're busy, but if you could\Njust pop in for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.25,0:11:57.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! I don't know how long\NI can stay, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:11:59.55,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go talk to my manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.16,0:12:02.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks very much.\NI'm glad I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:03.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They bring it on themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:07.73,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Soldiers fight because they like it, so when\Nthey get hurt, they brought it on themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:08.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.44,0:12:09.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Miss Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.61,0:12:11.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're starting the test for scene 12!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:12.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.73,0:12:13.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:14.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.17,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope this'll cheer him up a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:27.72,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major!\NMajor Focker!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:29.02,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Focker here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:31.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A single enemy ship is closing in at high speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:34.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Global has ordered a scramble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:36.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please return immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:40.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!\NOh, hey, don't tell Hikaru about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:44.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing him, he might push his luck\Nand try to launch too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:46.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:50.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And tell Kakizaki and Max to\Nstick with my team.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:51.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:04.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, are you sure we\Nshouldn't lift off?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:07.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't finished loading the supplies yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.45,0:13:09.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just see how things go\Nfor the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But don't let them get near the Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:12.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.58,0:13:23.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood? Once the enemy I indicate\Nhas appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:26.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,you are not to engage him under\Nany circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.65,0:13:30.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just make sure that he and l\Ncan face off, one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:33.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.\NLeave it to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:41.01,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Vermilion Two and Three, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:41.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:41.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&}Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:51.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Windsor Squadron, get ready to launch next!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:52.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:56.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting back to normal.\NJust relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.24,0:13:58.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your engines are up and running.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:13:59.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:05.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Skull Leader, ready to launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:08.05,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, try to keep the enemy\Naway from the Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:10.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that! I'm looking forward\Nto some pineapple salad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:14.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain? What is "pineapple salad" code for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Pineapple salad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:26.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major!\NWhere did you run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.35,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here and there...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:31.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, listen up! Your boss isn't here,\Nso you'd better stay sharp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:32.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.\NUnderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.09,0:14:33.98,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:38.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!\N{\i1}ATTACK!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.04,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:47.49,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, which one of these\Nis their ace pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.50,0:15:13.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:15.79,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:23.27,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:36.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He dodged my attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's acting strangely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.25,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what I was thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:46.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think they should be sending\Ncraft toward the Macross?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.85,0:15:49.08,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want them to,\Nbut you're exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:52.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if they're only targeting\NVermilion Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Lt. Max to clear out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:55.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Clear out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:59.22,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If their command ship moves to pursue\Nthen you may well be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:02.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy's after Max?\NWhy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:05.74,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know. But based on our observations,\Nthat's what we think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:07.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!\NWe'll find out soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.15,0:16:10.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max!\NRetreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:11.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:13.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the enemy's after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:14.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.28,0:16:23.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:31.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking better than I'd imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:33.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lying around in bed.\NI'm jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:35.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a bad room at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:42.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Sorry, but I slipped out in-between\Nsetups so I couldn't buy you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:46.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about that.\NAnyway, how'd you know I was in the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:48.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The Major told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:49.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai did?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:51.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a thoughtful man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:54.51,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sit down for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:56.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you been sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,About two hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.13,0:17:00.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:02.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be so hard if it\Nwere just the movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.58,0:17:05.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but there are press interviews, and\NI'm called out to all sorts of parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like there isn't enough\Nof me to go around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:13.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, is Kaifun in your kung fu movie too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:14.36,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:17.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaifun's an expert at Chinese\Nmartial arts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:19.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why the director took a liking to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.83,0:17:20.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:34.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it, move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.43,0:17:52.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.29,0:17:54.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:17:58.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's headed right for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:01.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Seal all entrances into the Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.35,0:18:32.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:40.75,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy unit has entered the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:44.24,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone outside, please take shelter\Nin the nearest building!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:03.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:16.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing?\NImpossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.44,0:19:21.08,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"But let me tell you something:\Nthe Macross has an ace pilot of its own!"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.00,0:19:24.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Open all ship's hatches!\NChase him out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.44,0:19:42.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Vermilion Three! The enemy has\Nlost interest in fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:44.24,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Halt pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:48.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.06,0:19:51.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I will redeem myself of\Nthis disgrace. Count on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.28,0:19:59.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!\NThey've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:02.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, you're nosing down.\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:06.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.\NWhat about Max?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:08.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He almost took out their command unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:09.75,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:11.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Returning to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.58,0:20:12.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.57,0:20:16.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!\NHere she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:18.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay!\NWake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:20.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:22.07,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't "Manager" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.31,0:20:25.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't come back on time, and now\Nthe whole shoot's off schedule!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:30.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NDid you see a man in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.28,0:20:31.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.46,0:20:32.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:36.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What if some weird rumors got started\Nabout you sleeping in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:37.84,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!\N Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.97,0:20:40.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!\NFine, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:53.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He got shot up bad this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.92,0:20:58.44,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.\NThis thing is really messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:23.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru sure is lucky.\NHe's got a real ace on his team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:24.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:27.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.98,0:21:32.15,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The pineapple salad will be ready in a minute.\NWhy don't you have a drink while you're waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:34.48,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I already have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.93,0:21:43.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All done!\N Sorry for the...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:44.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.75,0:21:49.96,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You drunk already?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:05.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.00,0:22:06.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.22,0:22:58.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.80,0:23:00.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Focker is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:07.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dead...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.65,0:23:12.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now... \NIn this same hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:21.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.59,0:23:23.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.42,0:23:35.42,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(77,107)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.42,0:23:35.42,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(332,456)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.46,0:23:42.82,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Global is contacted by a government\Nwilling to take in the refugees,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:45.97,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,and orders the Macross to set\Na course for North America.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:50.55,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,But when the Macross comes under attack by\NKamujin just prior to reaching its destination,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:54.00,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,it responds by setting the Omni-Directional\NBarrier to full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.67,0:23:57.96,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.24,0:24:00.03,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"BURST POINT"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.76,0:24:02.43,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(92,138)}BURST POINT
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.60,0:24:23.15,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.53,0:24:29.87,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.21,0:24:36.52,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running until the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:44.30,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.54,0:24:50.90,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.24,0:24:56.89,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.17,0:25:04.42,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.67,0:25:15.70,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
